 technologies?</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\">What are the different types of cookies?</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\">What are cookies used for?</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\">How does Marie Claire Armenia use cookies?</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\">How can users manage or opt out of cookies?</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\">Contact details and further information.</li></ul><h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:rgb(44, 62, 80);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:20px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">What Are Cookies and Similar Technologies?</h2><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:15px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">A cookie is a small data file, often including a unique identifier, that is sent to your device (e.g., computer, mobile phone, or tablet) by a web server. Cookies help websites remember information about your browsing activity and preferences. They collect information such as your device’s IP address, browser type, and the URL of the linking page if you arrived via a third-party site. If you register for any Services or subscribe, cookies may also collect your name and email address for verification purposes.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:15px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Similar technologies, such as local storage, web beacons, and pixels, perform similar functions and may also be used to enhance your experience on our Services. In this policy, references to cookies include these similar technologies.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:15px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Cookies help us analyze your use of our Services and improve your user experience by tailoring content and advertising to your interests.</p><h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:rgb(44, 62, 80);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:20px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">What Are the Different Types of Cookies?</h2><ul><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Temporary cookies that are deleted when you close your browser.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> Cookies that remain on your device for a set period after the browser is closed, allowing us to recognize you on future visits.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>First-Party Cookies:</strong> Cookies set directly by our website.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>Third-Party Cookies:</strong> Cookies set by external services, such as analytics providers or advertisers.</li></ul><h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:rgb(44, 62, 80);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:20px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">What Are Cookies Used For?</h2><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:15px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Marie Claire Armenia and trusted partners use cookies for the following purposes:</p><ul><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for the functioning of our Services. These cookies do not store personal information and expire after your session ends.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>Functional Cookies:</strong> Enhance user experience by remembering your preferences and settings.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>Analytical Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how users interact with our Services by tracking metrics such as page views and user behavior. This data is anonymized and used for statistical purposes.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>Targeting Cookies:</strong> Provide tailored advertising based on your browsing history and inferred interests.</li